<br>
5. This is main pet peeve of mine when in groups or raid situations..... a mob attacks you or your pet-- pet aggros on mob and begins attacking mob with the mob returning in kind attacking pet now ya begin pounding your pet backoff hot key and still mob keeps attacking pet while Enchanter screams at you to get yer pet off mob he is trying to mez and to no avail as mob keeps attacking your pet and this of course causes him to attack back. Give us a 5 or 6 second de-aggro period where pet wont aggro on a mob when ya give command to backoff either that or give us a &quot;true neutrel&quot; command where pet wont attack even if damaged of if you are attacked. Would be welcome to any pet class can assure you and since these are &quot;pets&quot; should be able to exert that level control on a &quot;mindless&quot; being.<br>
